source.name: USDA Database for the Isoflavone Content of Selected Foods, Release 2.0
source.description: This database contains data on the isoflavone content of 557 food items. Isoflavones included in the database are daidzein, genistein, glycitein and total isoflavones. Other phytoestrogens included in the database are coumestrol, biochanin A, and formononetin.
